Here is the summary of what I found while googling LDA software.

List of LDA programs:
	* GibbsLDA++: A C/C++ Implementation of Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA) using Gibbs Sampling for Parameter Estimation and Inference: http://gibbslda.sourceforge.net/
	* JGibbLDA: A Java Implementation of Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA) using Gibbs Sampling for Parameter Estimation and Inference: http://jgibblda.sourceforge.net/
	* plda: A parallel C++ implementation of fast Gibbs sampling of Latent Dirichlet Allocation: http://code.google.com/p/plda/
	* Mallet
